# Fixture directory for EndToEndIntegrationTests.
#
# This directory is:
#   - Picked up by xcodegen as a resource folder for the LiquidEditorTests
#     target (see project.yml).
#   - Left empty in source control on purpose. `FixtureFactory.swift`
#     generates `sample_video.mp4` and `sample_audio.wav` at runtime into
#     the test-process tmp directory, so no binaries are committed.
#
# If you drop a `sample_video.mp4` or `sample_audio.wav` here, FixtureFactory
# will prefer the bundled file over runtime generation.
